A list of introduction resources to learn Streaming and Apache Flink

Beginner:
1. Blog - Streaming101: https://www.oreilly.com/ideas/the-world-beyond-batch-streaming-101
2. Blog - Streaming102: https://www.oreilly.com/ideas/the-world-beyond-batch-streaming-102 
3. Blog series - Introduction to Flink Streaming
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-1/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-2/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-3/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-5/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-6/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-7/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-8/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-9/
  http://blog.madhukaraphatak.com/introduction-to-flink-streaming-part-10/

Intermediate:
4. Web - Introduction to Apache Flink: https://flink.apache.org/introduction.html
5. Book - Introduction to Apache Flink by Ellen Friedman & Kostas Tzoumas (pdf can be found via google search)

Experienced:
6. Book - Stream Processing with Apache Flink by Fabian Hueske & Vasiliki Kalavri (preview available; book coming out in July 2018)
7. Flink bi-annual conference: https://flink-forward.org/ (videos can be viewed via YouTube)
